That's only LH + Nethermind  <@412614104222531604> To just keep the full graffiti of the LH ones, hacky hack hack:

```python
def simplify_graffiti(graffiti_orig):
    if "lighthouse" in graffiti_orig:
        return graffiti_orig
    elif "-" in graffiti_orig:
        return graffiti_orig.split("-")[0]
    else:
        return graffiti_orig
